verbose_text: This was accompanied by a very modest decrease of Nanog and Oct4 in the Dusp6 KD, which could reflect the fact we only obtained a low level of KD (40% KD) in these cells and suggests that differentiation in the mEpiSCs Dusp6-KD is likely due to increased levels of FGF / ERK as it is already known that Dusp6 counteracts ERK signalling.
